Moon Potion.description:
)



When you drink this potion, you transform into a beast.<br />The designated beast can be distinguished with the identify spell, or can be understood by the smoke’s shape it produces when opened.<br />Your statistics change with the beast’s, but you retain your Intelligence and personality.<br />You can’t cast spells or concentrate on them if you cast them before.<br />Your gear melts into your new form, and you stay like this for 10 minutes.<br />
