Scheherazade’s Mirror.description:
)

This magic mirror’s back is made of jade and gold.<br />While holding the mirror, you can speak the command word and cast following spells by spending the necessary charge: comprehend languages (1), disguise self (1), alter self (2), suggestion (2), tongues (3), legend lore (5).<br />
The mirror has 10 charges, and it regains 1d8+2 expended charges daily at dawn.<br />
